The '''Zuliria Museum of Antiquities''' was a permanent institution in [[Zuliria]] dedicated to acquisition, conservation, research, communication and exhibition, for purposes of study, education, enjoyment, the tangible and intangible evidence of people of Zuliria and their environment.<ref name="AIR">''[[Alliance Intelligence Reports]]''</ref>

[[Arcona/Legends|Arcona]] student [[Ther-das]] worked in the Ancient Weapon department of this museum while trying to be re-accepted at [[Lerct Historical Institute/Legends|Lerct Historical Institute]] to get a degree in ancient weaponry. Ther-Das eventually became acquiition manager of the whole Museum.<ref name="AIR" />

Duelist aficionado [[Cene Gilvent]] also worked in this Museum, in property maintenance, and she spent seven years using the museum's resources to learn different fencing styles. Gilvent met Ther-Das while working in the museum.<ref name="AIR" />

